cal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_agency_hololive_production_first_english_conversation_instructional_book_holo_listening_to_be_released_on_september_29" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/vtuber_agency_hololive_production_first_english_conversation_instructional_book_holo_listening_to_be_released_on_september_29.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/vtuber_agency_hololive_production_first_english_conversation_instructional_book_holo_listening_to_be_released_on_september_29.jpg" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/vtuber_agency_hololive_production_first_english_conversation_instructional_book_holo_listening_to_be_released_on_september_29.jpg" alt="VTuber Office Hololive Productions首本英语会话教材《Holo Sling》9月29日发布" class="wp-image-95148"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p> “Holo Listening <strong>Holo</strong> Live English -Myth-，<strong>在</strong>神秘的世界中学习英语会话！” Takanashi Kiara、 <strong>Ninomae</strong> Ina&#39;nis、 <strong>Gawr Gura</strong><strong>和 Watson Amelia</strong>的《 <strong>Holo Live English -Myth-</strong> 》英语会话教科书 它是。</p><p>本书教材的故事由荣获2020年度Jump小说新人奖主题类金奖、长篇小说《等待凉波亚美》<strong>的涂田和穗</strong>负责。另外，纸质书附有5人录制的音频CD。您可以在欣赏达人对话的同时，享受地道的发音。</p><p>插图由纳森老师绘制，他因《Yuruyuri》和《Omuroya》的封面而广受欢迎，并为 Hololive<strong>创作</strong>了大量插图。另外，正文的插图由负责 Hololive 的邮票和各种商品的变形插图的<strong>Panjamu no Name</strong>先生负责。 </p><p></p><div class="dhypt649ab7085708e" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
